Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:38.21,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:41.63,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.97,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:49.14,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:01:01.93,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}话不投机 有些后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:03.88,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}流下眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:09.21,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}心随着急切的情感变乱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:16.52,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}调整情绪 想知道真实的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:22.27,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}执着于达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:25.95,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}重要的事物在不觉间模糊 溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:31.67,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}今天是崭新的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:37.10,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:40.70,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:44.04,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:48.13,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:51.76,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}一毫米的距离也觉得遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.83,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}匆匆走过的青春岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:59.10,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}不会忘 也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.86,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}留下闪耀的一页
